{"tid":333866,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國網友不孤單！俄羅斯下議院立法禁止VPN","createTime":"2017-07-24T08:27:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-25T07:18:59.000Z","uid":70917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"545876f715ed51589da5f54995e86c79c6e46b2b","tid":333866,"uid":70917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T08:27:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phphDXsTd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phphDXsTd.jpg&h=7c9db330&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國了封鎖VPN讓中國網友崩潰，直呼是「不讓人活」、「閉關鎖國，夢回大清」，然而中國網友不再孤單，俄國下議院為了要防範恐怖行動，一致通過新法將要禁止VPN。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，俄羅斯下議院「國家杜馬」在21日一致通過法案，將要禁止使用虛擬私人網路（VPN），也無法在匿名使用社交網路與軟體，只要上議院「俄羅斯聯邦委員會」通過該法案，俄國總統普廷簽名後，大約明年1月就會開始實施新法。<br />\n<br />\n議員指出，設立法案的目的是「禁止閱覽違法網站」與「因應恐怖行動」，但反普廷派認為這根本就是壓迫言論自由。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2141232\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2141232&d=x0yWNbEqvyDcxXsqcTbZ9YM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=205c95ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2141232&h=1fa9303c\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2141232</a>"},{"pid":"898360541aff7d44c6c432a71dbf6a705c2f0954","tid":333866,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T08:40:42.000Z","msg":"願意收養俄妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"153515d7cbabb396be9ed5ed7c72c6488dc4e890","tid":333866,"uid":9594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T07:18:59.000Z","msg":"中俄想做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}